00:07:53,474 --> 00:07:54,475
Nice save.

103
00:08:08,499 --> 00:08:11,483
Detective, what a surprise!

104
00:08:11,507 --> 00:08:14,476
You must have a guardian angel

105
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,475
