106
00:08:16,499 --> 00:08:18,477
Ready for your next riddle?

107
00:08:18,501 --> 00:08:19,491
No! No more riddles!

108
00:08:19,515 --> 00:08:21,489
What do you want, you maniac?

109
00:08:21,513 --> 00:08:23,497
'I prefer brainiac.'

110
00:08:23,521 --> 00:08:28,522
As you've been learning knowledge is power.

111
00:08:50,549 --> 00:08:52,533
Thud.

112
00:08:53,541 --> 00:08:54,551
'Your other left.'

