Everything in me is ancient?"

119
00:09:32,589 --> 00:09:34,571
These riddles hurt my brain!

120
00:09:34,595 --> 00:09:37,568
Chief, we located Yin heading for the museum.

121
00:09:37,592 --> 00:09:39,576
"Everything in me is ancient?"

122
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:44,586
Ah, how did she get museum out of that?

