00:10:02,613 --> 00:10:04,602
'But if you don't solve the next riddle soon'

127
00:10:04,626 --> 00:10:08,600
'the entire city block will be blown back to the ice age.'

128
00:10:08,624 --> 00:10:10,632
You better hope I don't solve it, Riddler

129
00:10:11,611 --> 00:10:12,594
because I'm going to find you

130
00:10:12,618 --> 00:10:13,608
