131
00:10:13,632 --> 00:10:17,598
You couldn't be further from the truth, detective.

132
00:10:17,622 --> 00:10:20,606
Oh, now, you're boring me.

133
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:22,616
On to the final riddle.

134
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,622
'A man builds a house'

135
00:10:23,646 --> 00:10:26,618
'with all four sides facing North.'

136
