137
00:10:29,641 --> 00:10:31,644
What color is the bear?

138
00:10:34,635 --> 00:10:35,634
Facing North?

139
00:10:35,658 --> 00:10:38,642
'What color is the bear?'

140
00:10:39,641 --> 00:10:42,625
Knowledge is power.

141
00:10:42,649 --> 00:10:44,634
Pity about your hard drive over here.

142
00:10:44,658 --> 00:10:46,628
You're ice cold.

143
00:10:46,652 --> 00:10:48,644
You couldn't be further from the truth, detective.

144
00:10:48,668 --> 00:10:52,633
Oh, now, you're boring me.

145
00:10:52,657 --> 00:10:53,648
Boring.

146
00:10:53,672 --> 00:10:54,676
Like a drill.

147
00:10:55,655 --> 00:10:57,648
Riddler can't resist leaving riddles

