00:11:12,695 --> 00:11:14,666
This riddle has no answer.

155
00:11:14,690 --> 00:11:16,674
- Riddler cheated? - Riddler quit.

156
00:11:16,698 --> 00:11:18,691
He's through playing.

157
00:11:21,683 --> 00:11:22,672
Dessert gelatin?

158
00:11:22,696 --> 00:11:25,674
Riddler's been leading us away from the main course

159
00:11:25,698 --> 00:11:27,685
further from the truth, all night long.

160
00:11:27,709 --> 00:11:28,686
Which is?

161
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:32,672
Beneath the last place we'd think to look..

162
00:11:32,696 --> 00:11:33,712
Again.

163
00:11:49,718 --> 00:11:50,702
Almost done?

164
00:11:50,726 --> 00:11:54,692
Just a few more gigabytes, Riddler sir.

165
00:11:54,716 --> 00:11:56,703
Then drain the brain.

166
00:11:56,727 --> 00:11:58,723
'Freeze, Riddler!'

167
00:12:00,725 --> 00:12:01,716
Knowledge is power, huh?

168
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:03,721
A fitting heist for a brainiac

169
00:12:03,745 --> 00:12:05,724
don't you think, Yinsy?

170
00:12:05,748 --> 00:12:08,726
If I need money boom, instant access

171
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:10,723
to Gotham's bank account numbers.

172
00:12:10,747 --> 00:12:13,727
If I want to shut down Gotham's transportation grid

173
00:12:13,751 --> 00:12:17,717
boom, instant access to the technical specs.

174
00:12:17,741 --> 00:12:19,724
Information!

175
00:12:19,748 --> 00:12:22,737
It's all here in the city's mainframe

176
00:12:22,761 --> 00:12:26,765
