177
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:30,772
But aren't you the smart detective

178
00:12:31,752 --> 00:12:34,732
to see the riddles within my riddles?

179
00:12:34,756 --> 00:12:35,739
We can trade IQ scores

180
00:12:35,763 --> 00:12:36,755
when you're behind bars, Riddler.

181
00:12:36,779 --> 00:12:41,739
Would that be your IQ or The Batman's?

182
00:12:41,763 --> 00:12:43,757
- I don't know what you're tal... - Please!

183
00:12:43,781 --> 00:12:45,749
Do you think I went to all the trouble

184
00:12:45,773 --> 00:12:48,755
to distract Gotham PD from my real crime?

185
00:12:48,779 --> 00:12:51,765
It was The Batman who concerned me.

186
00:12:51,789 --> 00:12:54,780
Isn't that right, Batman?

187
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:00,789
The game ends now, Riddler.

188
00:13:02,790 --> 00:13:05,774
I'll say, for the two of you.

189
00:13:05,798 --> 00:13:07,776
Gotham's infamous <i>vigilante</i>

190
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:10,768
working hand-in-hand with a cop?

191
00:13:10,792 --> 00:13:11,812
Scandalous.

192
00:13:23,824 --> 00:13:25,814
Tell me, Batman..

193
00:13:26,824 --> 00:13:30,820
What question can you never answer yes to?

194
00:13:33,828 --> 00:13:37,820
Are you asleep?

195
00:13:46,844 --> 00:13:50,840
Ah, look who decided to join the party.

196
00:13:53,848 --> 00:13:55,857
Welcome to my lair, Batman

197
00:13:56,836 --> 00:13:57,836
where questions are answers

198
00:13:57,860 --> 00:14:00,838
and Yin is yang.

199
00:14:00,862 --> 00:14:02,840
Cute, Riddler. Where are we?

200
00:14:02,864 --> 00:14:06,831
Why, the same place you've been all night long, Yinsy..

201
00:14:06,855 --> 00:14:08,844
Inside my brain.

202
00:14:08,868 --> 00:14:12,834
Stop speaking in riddles. Why are we here?

203
00:14:12,858 --> 00:14:14,852
