232
00:15:52,954 --> 00:15:54,944
'Chief Rojas, the entire City Hall database'

233
00:15:54,968 --> 00:15:56,944
'was stolen earlier tonight.'

234
00:15:56,968 --> 00:15:59,968
But we were there! Is this a joke?

235
00:16:00,969 --> 00:16:02,985
So you do have a day job.

236
00:16:03,964 --> 00:16:07,963
