240
00:16:14,989 --> 00:16:16,975
- You don't know. - I do know. He's...

241
00:16:16,999 --> 00:16:20,959
No! No, no, no, you'll ruin my game!

242
00:16:20,983 --> 00:16:23,972
The true identity of The Batman is Ethan Bennett.

243
00:16:23,996 --> 00:16:26,007
Duh, I can't hear you!

244
00:16:26,986 --> 00:16:30,001
Riddler, the answer to am I a policeman..

245
00:16:31,994 --> 00:16:33,003
Yes.

246
00:16:50,029 --> 00:16:53,018
No one outsmarts The Riddler!

247
00:17:08,035 --> 00:17:11,011
We are in Riddler's brain.

248
00:17:11,035 --> 00:17:13,024
