261
00:18:52,152 --> 00:18:54,122
Hm, and here I thought

262
00:18:54,146 --> 00:18:57,139
this was going to be a battle of wits.

263
00:19:07,149 --> 00:19:08,134
Pretty swift, Yin.

264
00:19:08,158 --> 00:19:10,137
Maybe one day you'll put that big brain of yours

265
00:19:10,161 --> 00:19:13,135
